<span id="freeTextContainer11279350066770557164"><strong>Inspiring motivation</strong><br/><br/>It&apos;s quite possible that I highlighted more in this book than most others I&apos;ve read. Point after point resonated with my own recent journey to discover passions, learn more about a craft, and expand my vision to have more meaning in what I do. I would highly recommend this book to everyone.</span>
  <span id="freeText11279350066770557164" style="display:none"><strong>Inspiring motivation</strong><br /><br />It's quite possible that I highlighted more in this book than most others I've read. Point after point resonated with my own recent journey to discover passions, learn more about a craft, and expand my vision to have more meaning in what I do. I would highly recommend this book to everyone.</span>
